column2: SELECT s.ObjID as #objid, s.ra, s.dec, s.l, s.b, s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u as u0, s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g as g0, s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r as r0, (s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u) - (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) as umg, (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) - (s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r) as gmr, sp.LOGGADOP as logg, sp.LOGGADOPUNC as logg_err, sp.FEHADOP as feh, sp.FEHADOPUNC as feh_err, sp.ELODIERVFINAL as vr, sp.ELODIERVFINALERR as vr_err INTO mydb.hyllus_off2_spec_rgbs FROM Star s JOIN sppParams sp ON s.ObjID = sp.BESTOBJID WHERE (s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g) - (s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_r) > # AND sp.LOGGADOP > # AND sp.LOGGADOP < # AND sciencePrimary = # AND s.ra > # - #*s.dec +#*s.dec*s.dec AND s.ra < # - #*s.dec +#*s.dec*s.dec AND s.dec > # AND s.dec < #
